  <text>
    <body xml:base="urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.1st1K-eng1">
      <div type="book" n="1">
        <div type="section" n="1">
          <p>
            <s/>Thucydides, an Athenian, wrote the history of the war.
            <s/>He began the task at the very outset of the war.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div type="section" n="2">
          <p>
            <s/>For this was the greatest movement that had ever stirred the Hellenes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
